    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and has clearly been well-taken care of over the years. You\u2019ll find it clean, running smoothly, and ready for many more road trips. It\u2019s got that perfect balance of being well-loved but still looking great and feeling tight on the road. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
