      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a limited-slip rear differential. The chassis has been properly sorted, including proactive reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The suspension maintains its factory-spec geometry, providing the communicative feedback and precise turn-in characteristic of the M-tuned MacPherson/multi-link arrangement. Recent technical service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and a cooling system refresh. While the exterior shows minor signs of use, the drivetrain is mechanically synchronized, pulling hard to its 8,000 RPM redline with linear power delivery. A mechanically sorted, driver-focused icon ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
